				<table width="100%" cellspacing="5">
				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Almost everything takes an immediate effect, since it uses less hardware. About the only delayed things are those that affect the periods of timers, since it takes less hardware to reload the count on zero rather than compare the count with the period to see if it's equal or greater (as some other sound chips do, like the YM-2149 and AY-8910).</div>

